metadata.name: Hallucinationatory Dreamscape
metadata.description: Hallucinationatory Dreamscape is a captivating artwork that delves into the realm of hypnagogic hallucinations and surreal dreams. The central figure, adorned with a grass hat and wearing clothing reminiscent of art and costume history, gazes ahead with a wounded yet fiercely wild face. A red rose adorns their attire, contrasting against the dimly colored, dreamlike surroundings
